com.pstmetro.generics

Class ArraySet<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pstmetro.generics.ArraySet<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - Type of objects stored within the Array
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<V>, Collection<V>, Set<V>

    public class ArraySet<V>
extends Object
implements Set<V>
    The ArraySet class is merely a custom implementation of a set that is backed by an Array. We created this class to prove that we are able to create efficient Data structures.
